Package: mvPot
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate Peaks-over-Threshold Modelling for Spatial Extreme Events
Version: 0.1.5
Date: 2019-06-25
Authors@R: c(person(given="Raphael", family="de Fondeville", email = "raphael.de-fondeville@epfl.ch",  role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person(given="Leo", family="Belzile", role = "aut", email = "belzilel@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9135-014X")),
             person(given="Emeric", family="Thibaud", role = "ctb"))
Description: Tools for high-dimensional peaks-over-threshold inference and simulation
  of spatial extremal processes. Key references include de Fondeville and Davison (2018) <doi:10.1093/biomet/asy026>, Thibaud and Opitz (2015) <doi:10.1093/biomet/asv045>, Wadsworth and Tawn <doi:10.1093/biomet/ast042> as well as Genz and Bretz (2009) <doi:10.1007/978-3-642-01689-9>.
